<section class="pillars">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Cosa troverai qui</h2>
      <p>Tre pilastri per capire perché prendi decisioni finanziarie sbagliate — e come rimediare.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
            <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#c9a84c" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M14 20 C14 16, 20 12, 26 16 C32 20, 26 28, 20 24" stroke="#c9a84c" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <circle cx="14" cy="20" r="2" fill="#c9a84c"/>
            <circle cx="26" cy="16" r="2" fill="#c9a84c"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Psicologia del Denaro</h3>
        <p>Perché il tuo cervello ti frega quando si parla di soldi. Bias cognitivi, euristiche e trappole mentali che ti costano cari.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
            <rect x="8" y="8" width="24" height="24" rx="4" stroke="#c9a84c" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M14 20 L18 24 L26 16" stroke="#c9a84c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Finanza Comportamentale</h3>
        <p>Le regole non scritte che governano le tue scelte economiche. Dalla perdita avversione all'effetto gregge.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
            <path d="M20 6 L20 34 M6 20 L34 20" stroke="#c9a84c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="14" stroke="#c9a84c" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Strumenti Pratici</h3>
        <p>Checklist, framework e modelli per prendere decisioni migliori. Niente teoria — solo roba che funziona.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pillars {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--secondary);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .pillar-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pillars {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .pillars-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
